div.p: Group 1 Mapping from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Ingredient|5.0.0 to unspecified code system

tr.td: FHIR R5 Resource `Ingredient` is representable via FHIR R4 Resource `Basic`. Element `Ingredient` is not mapped to FHIR R4, since FHIR R5 `Ingredient` is not mapped.
